{"tid":377682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7-11奇聞：幫隻錶增值","createTime":"2017-08-28T00:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T15:45:47.000Z","uid":28938,"like":13,"dislike":880,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f69b43ae39e8186d46d61552f0d0ef4ab857dea2","tid":377682,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"尋晚有奇聞......笑Q死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事緣係咁既，尋晚同fd去 clubbing，大家都飲到貓貓地，諗住去7-11買支水醒一醒，之後就搭紅Van番歸。<br />\n<br />\n點知入到7-11果時，有個女人好大聲鬧個店員，話咩：「邊度無ar? 你玩野咩?一舊水唔夠兩舊水夠啦掛。」<br />\n<br />\n我同個fd都覺得奇怪，當堂醒左一醒，睇下咩事啦，原來條女都飲貓左，手挽住隻錶係咁係部八達通機度拍，頂原來係想同隻錶增值,，低Q能 ，增值之後會多幾個鐘頭駛咩 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更奇怪既事係之後發生，正當個店員同條女嘈緊果時，有個執緊貨既阿叔店員行左過黎。<br />\n<br />\n阿叔攞左條女果二百蚊，跟住同條女講：「唔好意思，個同事新黎既，唔識野。」 <br />\n<br />\n之後就唔知點拍部收銀機，整左d Do~既增值聲出黎，條女聽到聲之後就走左 。<br />\n<br />\n我同我個fd 當堂O 左嘴 ，間7-11咁就昆左條女200蚊，早知我用我部電話錄定d 增值既do do 聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉，飲醉左既人真係癡Q線的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf08e866e3554f264101191349aab5ea17162490","tid":377682,"uid":57554,"like":574,"dislike":13,"score":561,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:36:18.000Z","msg":"手錶八達通未聽過？"},{"pid":"4d0368880639a2eb12d52a3ba1af8b125318b3e5","tid":377682,"uid":27024,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a660bb07c283c80f5401143f05e608a11c38a5","tid":377682,"uid":35136,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n原來七仔咁無良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef122bfed6ce7ebd230d74648c2a9279e40c2e","tid":377682,"uid":125302,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"repl